songs.title: Cocoa Butter (Cross & Pic Interlude)

Man 2: Listen, I'm talking to remove something that you're insecure about! But listen man, are you insecure about anything on you? No! But there's women that's insecure about stretch marks!

You just say, you wanna hit someone. Is you gonna hit, the joint you put me on one time was beautiful. Which joint I put you on? listen but her stomach was a prune but I still kissed her!
